---
title: Turkey and Fig Burgers with Garlic and Onion Cream Cheese Spread
description: These turkey burgers get dressed up with an incredible cream cheese spread and fig jam to balance out the flavours and turn an ordinary dinner into an unforgettable feas!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/turkey-and-fig-burgers-a2d38a9d.jpg
